<topic id="blacklist">
    <title>Blacklist</title>
    <shortdesc>Blacklist is used to block an incoming/outgoing call.</shortdesc>
    <body>
        <p>If the number of incoming or outgoing call is listed in the
                <uicontrol>Blacklist</uicontrol>, the caller will hear the following prompt: “The
            number you have dialed is not in service. Please check the number and try again”. The
            system will then disconnect the call.</p>
        <section id="section_bvt_kky_zgb">
            <title>Block incoming/outgoing numbers</title>
            <p>
                <ol id="ol_gk4_mky_zgb">
                    <li>Go to <menucascade>
                            <uicontrol>Gateway</uicontrol>
                            <uicontrol>Gateway Settings</uicontrol>
                            <uicontrol>Blacklist</uicontrol>
                        </menucascade>.</li>
                    <li>Click <uicontrol>Add Blacklist</uicontrol>.</li>
                    <li>Configure the following settings.<p><image href="../image/add-blacklist.jpg"
                                width="650" id="image_f1d_3ly_zgb"/><ul id="ul_is4_3ly_zgb">
                                <li><uicontrol>ID</uicontrol>: </li>
                                <li><uicontrol>Number</uicontrol>: Enter the desired number. E.g.
                                    18855556666.</li>
                                <li><uicontrol>Type</uicontrol>: E.g. set the
                                        <uicontrol>Type</uicontrol> to
                                        <uicontrol>Inbound</uicontrol>. TA FXS gateway supports to
                                    block 3 types of numbers.<ul id="ul_vnq_zly_zgb">
                                        <li><b>Inbound</b>: The number would be disallowed to call
                                            in the system.</li>
                                        <li><b>Outbound</b>: The TA FXS gateway's extensions is
                                            disallowed to call the number out from the system.</li>
                                        <li><b>Both</b>: Both inbound and outbound calls are
                                            disallowed.</li>
                                    </ul></li>
                            </ul></p></li>
                    <li>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Apply
                            Changes</uicontrol>.<p>When the number 18855556666 reaches the TA FXS
                            gateway, the call will fail.</p></li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="section_z3z_tmy_zgb">
            <title>Delete the blacklist</title>
            <p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Go to <menucascade>
                            <uicontrol>Gateway</uicontrol>
                            <uicontrol>Gateway Settings</uicontrol>
                            <uicontrol>Blacklist</uicontrol>
                        </menucascade>.</li>
                    <li>Choose the desired number and click <uicontrol>Delete The
                            Selected</uicontrol>.<p><image href="../image/delete-blacklist.jpg"
                                width="650" id="image_dmt_hny_zgb"/></p></li>
                    <li>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Apply
                            Changes</uicontrol>.<p>When the number 18855556666 reaches the TA FXS
                            gateway again, the call will success.</p></li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </section>
    </body>
</topic>
